What is Kawhi Leonard's net worth?

Kawhi Leonard has made at least $328,300,910 playing professional basketball.

How much does Kawhi Leonard make?

Kawhi Leonard made $49,205,800 in 2025.

What does Kawhi Leonard average?

Kawhi Leonard averages 24.3 points, 5.7 rebounds, and 3.5 assists per game.

How many rings does Kawhi Leonard have?

Kawhi Leonard has won 2 championships.

What schools did Kawhi Leonard attend?

Kawhi Leonard attended King in Riverside, California and San Diego State.

What are Kawhi Leonard's nicknames?

The Claw, Board Man, Fun Guy, The Hand, The Terminator are nicknames for Kawhi Leonard.

Is Kawhi Leonard injured?

Kawhi Leonard is listed as Out (Ankle) - The Clippers listed Leonard as Out for Thursday's (Nov. 20) game against the Magic.
